&lt;li class="MsoNormal" style="color: black; text-align: justify; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in; vertical-align: middle;"&gt;&lt;span lang="ES-CR" style="font-family: 'Delivery',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: ES-CR;"&gt;Manejo de Internet y protocolos de transferencia.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in; vertical-align: middle;"&gt;&lt;span lang="ES-CR" style="font-family: 'Delivery',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: ES-CR;"&gt;Manejo de Microsoft Office a nivel avanzado, Paquetes / módulos Visual Studio, XML, Access.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
